情熱のFitとDevelop
There are two mindsets of [passion].
	Fit: Meet the object of your passion
	Develop: Passion grows over time as you do it.
I used to refer to the former thought as "the idea that [the prince on the white horse] should come someday," but I never explained it in terms of a contrasting structure.

	[Let's stop advising people to "find your passion" - Taka Umada - Medium https://medium.com/@tumada/do-not-find-your-passion-a7b2f290b5a]

This is related to the story of [values are verbalized from the bottom up] introduced in [The Art of Intellectual Production of Engineers].
	[(2.2.4.2) Values are verbalized bottom-up].
